{"tid":2242653,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個 同老豆老母最深刻既回憶","createTime":"2020-10-14T07:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T12:24:54.000Z","uid":142523,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c86df0dfe12e70c43d979222f383a2794ee14c97","tid":2242653,"uid":142523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"我3歲老豆老母離左婚<br />\n老豆移居內地 甚少見面<br />\n係小一既時侯 佢帶左我返去同佢渡過一個長假期<br />\n佢介紹左佢新女朋友比我識<br />\n仲記得岩岩見面果陣我好怕羞面紅<br />\n唔敢講野 因為隱約記得佢好靚 好有氣質<br />\n<br />\n因為老豆要返工 所以由佢負責湊我<br />\n果陣我唔識講普通話 佢又唔識廣東話<br />\n雞同鴨講 我大概估到佢問我想食d咩<br />\n於是我劃左幅餐蛋麵比佢睇 然後佢好開心咁笑一笑<br />\n呢種感覺真係好神奇<br />\n<br />\n又有一日佢又同埋佢朋友(都係好靚)一齊帶我去<br />\n公園玩, 我玩到好攰然後挨落佢膊頭到<br />\n佢又好似真係當我係仔咁摸我個頭<br />\n果刻我真係以為自己有返個老母<br />\n<br />\n又有一晚因為我細個好怕黑，我唔敢自己一間房訓<br />\n我流哂馬尿求老豆比我同佢地一齊訓<br />\n我仲識得搞下氣氛 同佢女朋友講左句<br />\n不如你做我媽咪啦 佢笑到見牙唔見眼<br />\n但我記得老豆講左句&quot;痴線!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n遺憾既係 長假期完結後<br />\n我正正要離開時，我係老豆架車到望返轉頭<br />\n見到佢喊哂口 又不斷求我老豆比我留低<br />\n又因為我同老豆嗌交 睇得出佢真係好唔捨得<br />\n大個左 我先知道 原來幸福真係唔係必然<br />\n亦都證實我父母緣份淺薄<br />\n<br />\n亦注定我呢世都係個孤兒仔。"},{"pid":"f46b105abc330134faeda7d3b069dc004f62f33f","tid":2242653,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"最後你後母點"},{"pid":"21e4c9f82772e9662d99dc7192820072d844809f","tid":2242653,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"以為扑埋後母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b9624ba1a552e4225234ec54d535bd62bc702b","tid":2242653,"uid":142523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e4c9f82772e9662d99dc7192820072d844809f","tid":2242653,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"以為扑埋後母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"果陣得小一 扯旗都未識啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9452b7a2a42907f085ad4041fb19c7faa084024","tid":2242653,"uid":142523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46b105abc330134faeda7d3b069dc004f62f33f","tid":2242653,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"最後你後母點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔係後母 佢地只係維持左一段好短暫既男女朋友<br />\n只係我天真以為我真係有返個第二個老母"},{"pid":"fba7de607631833c4492dae81314c1e3ecfaa19f","tid":2242653,"uid":251961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"老母幾次拎菜刀追我，仲斬爆我個房門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因：佢老公外遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a31edf8abebe0ba5f2338fe5df50f3f3ebcc93","tid":2242653,"uid":352469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}